### Health
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health


### Register ROLE_USER
### Apres cette requete, copier le token/lien affiche dans les logs:
### DEV email verification link for user1@sgitu.ma: http://localhost:8080/auth/verify-email?token=...
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user1@sgitu.ma",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "ROLE_USER"
}


### Login avant verification email - attendu 401
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user1@sgitu.ma",
  "password": "123456"
}


### Verify email
GET http://localhost:8080/auth/verify-email?token=COLLER_EMAIL_VERIFICATION_TOKEN_ICI


### Login apres verification email
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user1@sgitu.ma",
  "password": "123456"
}


### Forgot password
### Copier ensuite le reset token affiche dans les logs:
### DEV password reset token for user1@sgitu.ma: ...
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user1@sgitu.ma"
}


### Reset password
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "COLLER_PASSWORD_RESET_TOKEN_ICI",
  "newPassword": "newPassword123"
}


### Login avec nouveau mot de passe
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user1@sgitu.ma",
  "password": "newPassword123"
}


### 401 - Route protegee sans JWT
GET http://localhost:8080/api/payments/1


### 404 - JWT valide mais route inconnue
GET http://localhost:8080/api/unknown/test
Authorization: Bearer COLLER_ACCESS_TOKEN_ICI
X-Correlation-Id: test-404


### 403 - ROLE_USER interdit sur route admin
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/users/1/roles
Authorization: Bearer COLLER_ACCESS_TOKEN_ICI
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: test-403

{
  "role": "ROLE_ADMIN"
}


