### Refresh token
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "COLLER_REFRESH_TOKEN_ICI"
}


### Logout
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer COLLER_ACCESS_TOKEN_ICI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "COLLER_REFRESH_TOKEN_ICI"
}
